data.description: Welcome to 722 Flint Ridge Dr, an immaculately maintained 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home, located just 10 minutes from downtown Nashville! This home boasts an open concept floor plan with custom finishes throughout its nearly 2,500 + sq ft interior. The gorgeous kitchen features all stainless steel appliances and a kitchen island opening up to the family room - perfect for entertaining! Upstairs includes a large Master Suite with double vanities, double shower heads and a spacious walk in closet as well as two guest bedrooms and the laundry. Step outside onto either of the two walk out decks and enjoy serene views of the wooded oasis right in your own backyard! Take advantage of instant equity with the 700 + sq ft of unfinished basement space, roughed in & ready for your extra living area and additional guest suite! Minutes to local conveniences and convenient to the interstate. New golf course opening FALL 2024 directly behind your backyard. Truly a must see!
